highlights.text: “おつかれSUMMER” by HALCALI has been on Viral Songs South Korea the longest, at 112 days straight.
“CLIMA LINDO - SLOWED” by GXMZ and Repsaj is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs South Korea, up 24 spots at #74.
Effie has the most spots on Viral Songs South Korea. “CAN I SIP 담배” is the highest at #9.
“MALVADO DE VAPO” by xccvdxz and Y3LLAVISION is the highest new entry on Viral Songs South Korea at #78.
